{"product_id":"naif-nurturing-night-cream-50ml","title":"NAIF Nurturing Night Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNaïf Nurturing Night Cream contributes to a good night's sleep. The regenerating night cream soothes the skin and supports the natural skin process. Includes almond oil, shea butter and macadamia extract for ultimate hydration and moisture retention. No more dry spots!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe cream absorbs quickly, doesn't stick and doesn't make the skin feel tight. So you don't have to worry when resting your head on your pillow. The night cream is made without mineral oils, microplastics and silicones.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe Naïf regenerating night cream is for every skin type. So also for the most sensitive skin. All Naïf products are vegan, made with a gentle fragrance, are dermatologically tested and do not contain the 26 most common allergens.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eA night cream is best applied if you apply a good, thick amount. Do this on clean, cleansed skin. And don't forget to apply it to the neck and décolleté. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua\/ Water, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Sweet Almond) Oil, Glycerin, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Macadamia Integrifolia Seed Oil, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Methylpropanediol, Linum Usitatissimum (Linseed) Seed Oil, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cetyl Alcohol, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Sucrose Stearate, Tocopherol, Helianthus Annuus, (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Xanthan Gum, Caprylyl Glycol, Phenylpropanol, Parfum\/Fragrance, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915767255367,"sku":null,"price":23.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-nurturing-night-cream-50ml-623217.png?v=1739897168","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/naif-nurturing-night-cream-50ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}